Package de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.supervisor

Record Class AgentReport

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.supervisor.AgentReport
Record Components:
attachedThings - a list of attached things to the agent
energy - the current energy level of the agent
deactivated - true if the agent is deactivated
actions - the set of actions the agent is able to perform
position - the position of the agent
distanceDispenser - the distance to all dispenser types
distanceGoalZone - the smallest distance to a goal zone
groupDesireType - the current group desire of the agent
step - the current step of the simulation
agentActionName - the name of the last action sent to the server
nearestGoalZone - the position of the nearest gaol zone
groupDesireBlock - the block type of the current group desire
public record AgentReport(List<massim.protocol.data.Thing> attachedThings, int energy, boolean deactivated, Set<String> actions, Point position, int[] distanceDispenser, int distanceGoalZone, String groupDesireType, int step, String agentActionName, int numOfDistinctGoalZones, Point nearestGoalZone, Point goalZone2, String groupDesireBlock, int distanceRoleZone) extends Record
The Record AgentReport provides a data structure to store important information about the agent.
Author:
Heinz Stadler
